[
  {
    "text": "Oh, sir, we found\nthe other stone.",
    "start": 0.8,
    "duration": 2.235
  },
  {
    "text": "Ooh! Let me see it!",
    "start": 3.035,
    "duration": 2.803
  },
  {
    "text": "Beautiful.\nThey're both mine.",
    "start": 5.838,
    "duration": 3.738
  },
  {
    "text": "Smiths, you're free to go.",
    "start": 9.576,
    "duration": 2.001
  },
  {
    "text": "Stan: Really?",
    "start": 9.576,
    "duration": 2.001
  },
  {
    "text": "At last, I'm ready\nto enter the final stage",
    "start": 11.577,
    "duration": 3.136
  },
  {
    "text": "of my grand design.",
    "start": 14.713,
    "duration": 2.736
  },
  {
    "text": "Okay, then.",
    "start": 17.449,
    "duration": 2.937
  },
  {
    "text": "My grand design,",
    "start": 17.449,
    "duration": 2.937
  },
  {
    "text": "it will change everything.",
    "start": 20.386,
    "duration": 2.169
  },
  {
    "text": "Uh-huh. We go out\nthe way we came?",
    "start": 22.555,
    "duration": 2.068
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah, it's two rights\nand then a left.",
    "start": 24.623,
    "duration": 1.669
  },
  {
    "text": "But you're really not\nin the least bit curious",
    "start": 26.292,
    "duration": 2.303
  },
  {
    "text": "about what I'm doing?",
    "start": 28.595,
    "duration": 1.467
  },
  {
    "text": "My grand design?",
    "start": 30.062,
    "duration": 2.77
  },
  {
    "text": "Not -- not particularly.",
    "start": 30.062,
    "duration": 2.77
  },
  {
    "text": "Okay. But I have to say,\nif you guys had a grand design,",
    "start": 32.832,
    "duration": 3.77
  },
  {
    "text": "I'd at least listen to it.",
    "start": 36.602,
    "duration": 1.569
  },
  {
    "text": "Of course, I've always\nbeen curious.",
    "start": 38.171,
    "duration": 1.934
  },
  {
    "text": "Even as a child, I took apart\nmy alarm clock",
    "start": 40.105,
    "duration": 2.437
  },
  {
    "text": "to see how it worked,\nbut that's me,",
    "start": 42.542,
    "duration": 2.769
  },
  {
    "text": "and you guys are you.",
    "start": 45.311,
    "duration": 1.368
  },
  {
    "text": "And, uh, I guess I gotta\nrespect that.",
    "start": 46.679,
    "duration": 3.17
  },
  {
    "text": "Well, then it's settled --",
    "start": 49.849,
    "duration": 2.302
  },
  {
    "text": "Seize them!",
    "start": 49.849,
    "duration": 2.302
  },
  {
    "text": "[ Clanks ]",
    "start": 52.151,
    "duration": 0.935
  }
]